<h1>Volunteer Preferences</h1>

<p>
  <%= virginia_first %> events need people with technical and non-technical backgrounds.
  There really is a job for everyone! By indicating which positions you
  would be interested in, our volunteer coordinators will be able to better
  match you up with a job you'll enjoy. If you would like to become more
  involved <%= virginia_first %>, look for our key
  positions<sup>&dagger;</sup>.
</p>

<%= simple_form_for @profile, url: volunteer_profile_path, html: { id: "edit_volunteer_profile", class: "form-horizontal" } do |f| %>
  <%= f.error_notification %>

  <%= render 'volunteer_fields', f: f %>

  <div class="form-actions">
    <%= f.button :submit, class: "btn-primary" %>
  </div>
<% end %>
